### Upload Component File Test
### POST /api/robot-configs/components
### 測試上傳機器人元件壓縮檔

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5253
@token = {{auth-test.http:authResponse.response.body.token}}

### 1. Upload a component ZIP file (gripper)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/robot-configs/components
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="gripper_component.zip"
Content-Type: application/zip

< ./test-files/sample_component.zip
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="componentType"

gripper
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

